---
layout: base
title: Research
permalink: /research/
---
<section class="page">
  <p>
    I build <strong>foundation models for spatial and physical intelligence</strong> — world models
    that perceive, simulate, and reason about the physical 3D world. I'm advised by
    <a href="{{ site.advisor }}">Dan Yamins</a> in the NeuroAI Lab at Stanford. Selected papers,
    grouped by theme:
  </p>

  {% for theme in publications.themes %}
    <h2 class="theme-title">{{ theme.name }}</h2>
    {% for p in theme.papers %}
      <div class="pub">
        <div class="pub-title">
          {% if p.arxiv %}<a href="{{ p.arxiv }}">{{ p.title }}</a>
          {% elif p.link %}<a href="{{ p.link }}">{{ p.title }}</a>
          {% else %}{{ p.title }}{% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if p.authors %}
          <div class="pub-authors">{{ p.authors | replace("Wanhee Lee", "<strong>Wanhee Lee</strong>") | safe }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="pub-venue">
          <span class="venue">{{ p.venue }}</span>{% if p.arxiv %} &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="{{ p.arxiv }}">arXiv</a>{% endif %}{% if p.project %} &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="{{ p.project }}">project page</a>{% endif %}{% if p.link and not p.arxiv %} &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="{{ p.link }}">pdf</a>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>
